'''Hardscrabble''' was a town on [[Muskree]] where the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] tiny population lived during the reign of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Hardscrabble would become home to several mining operations, due to several scans indicating a rich vein of minerals and ore. The scans proved false, however, with the settlers remaining taking up [[Nerf/Legends|nerf]] herding.

